## Objectives
Ensure that access to systems and data is authorized, appropriate, and monitored.

## Core Requirements
- Least privilege and need-to-know.
- MFA for remote admin and high-risk access.
- Joiner/Mover/Leaver processes with timely provisioning and deprovisioning.
- Quarterly access reviews for critical systems.
- Strong authentication and session controls.

## Monitoring & Review
- Centralized logging of access events.
- Periodic certification of roles and entitlements.
